verses.verse: Look! <WH1288> Praise Yahweh, <WH3068> all you servants <WH5650> of Yahweh, <WH3068> who stand <WH5975> by night <WH3915> in Yahweh <WH3068>'s house! <WH1004>
Lift up <WH5375> your hands <WH3027> in the sanctuary. <WH6944> Praise <WH1288> Yahweh! <WH3068>
May Yahweh <WH3068> bless <WH1288> you from Zion; <WH6726> even he who made <WH6213> heaven <WH8064> and earth. <WH776>
